Trade Marketing Supervisor
Responsibilities
To Calculate the STT & STD Plan breakdown by Area & Depo including Alloc Week 1 & Full Month, and monthly setting DRP Parameter Formula.To Generate Weekly OWA Report for Sales Dept, Supply Chain Dept, & Marketing Dept.To Generate the Monthly Bottom Up Rolling Forecast with Top Down Quarter Strategy.To Manage Monthly STT, STD, Stock Data for Sales, Operation, Marketing Meetings.To Generate Monthly Channel Analysis for Sales & Marketing Meeting.  Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree, Economics, Food & Beverage Services Management, Business Studies/Administration/Management, Marketing, or Commerce.Required skill(s): communication skill, Micorsoft Office.At least 2 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Applicants must be willing to work in Head Office at Cyber 2 Building - Jakarta.Preferably Supervisor / Coordinators.Full-Time position(s) available.
